  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  inpatient rehabilitation

          -  COPD (Gold stage III and IV)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe exacerbation in the last four weeks

          -  acute infections

          -  fever

          -  neuritides

          -  severe osteoporosis

          -  skin disease

          -  manic depression
      </textblock>
